{"tid":1739676,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方強調暴徒「走得一時唔走得一世」否認拖行 「其實佢有腳，佢可以行」不排除有人故意不合作希望拖延時間讓所謂「兄弟姊妹」救","createTime":"2019-11-19T16:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T19:28:49.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"61042be6681ee45a854283f85c39e0064a199951","tid":1739676,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:14:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/290963/%e3%80%90%e7%90%86%e5%a4%a7%e8%a1%9d%e7%aa%81%e3%80%91%e6%b1%9f%e6%b0%b8%e7%a5%a5%e7%a8%b1%e7%a4%ba%e5%a8%81%e8%80%85%e5%86%80%e7%8d%b2%e7%87%9f%e6%95%91%e3%80%8c%e5%a4%aa%e5%a4%a9%e7%9c%9f%e3%80%8d/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F290963%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e7%2590%2586%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e8%25a1%259d%25e7%25aa%2581%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%25b1%259f%25e6%25b0%25b8%25e7%25a5%25a5%25e7%25a8%25b1%25e7%25a4%25ba%25e5%25a8%2581%25e8%2580%2585%25e5%2586%2580%25e7%258d%25b2%25e7%2587%259f%25e6%2595%2591%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%25a4%25aa%25e5%25a4%25a9%25e7%259c%259f%25e3%2580%258d%2F&d=UXFjm%2BDMXm%2Fj1yL9MgXeqFDf25aqCgCAAhwKlvpwqyI%3D&h=dc8adeb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/290963/%e3%80%90%e7%90%86%e5%a4%a7%e8%a1%9d%e7%aa%81%e3%80%91%e6%b1%9f%e6%b0%b8%e7%a5%a5%e7%a8%b1%e7%a4%ba%e5%a8%81%e8%80%85%e5%86%80%e7%8d%b2%e7%87%9f%e6%95%91%e3%80%8c%e5%a4%aa%e5%a4%a9%e7%9c%9f%e3%80%8d/</a><br />\n<br />\n警方連日包圍理工大學，部分被困人士突破昨日重圍成功離開。警察公共關係科高級警司江永祥今日在記者會上強調，「走得一時，唔走得一世」，逃走的罪犯終有一日會被捕。<br />\n<br />\n有示威者昨日從行人天橋游繩而下，隨即坐上前來營救的電單車離開。江永祥表示，所謂到理大營救示威者的「接仔車」「校巴」，全部都是協助罪犯，「邊個向我哋使用暴力嘅話，我哋必然會用適當嘅方法，將佢哋制服同埋拘捕，情況就係咁簡單」。<br />\n<br />\n被問到有傳媒拍攝到警方拖行示威者，江永祥稱很多人不願起身行走，所以警方才要拖行，「其實佢有雙腳，佢係可以行嘅」。警方亦不排除有人是想故意不合作，希望拖延時間，讓所謂「兄弟姊妹」可以救他，「但呢啲全部都太天真，我話畀你聽，走得一時，唔走得一世」，前日被人營救的示威者最終都被警方拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n江永祥強調，「犯法嘅人逃走終有一日會畀人拘捕」，有傳媒形容示威者在理大「絕處逃生」，其實只是縱容與包庇罪犯。"},{"pid":"fb94938297311ebf4cdea08e9076c139529d73c9","tid":1739676,"uid":118700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:17:40.000Z","msg":"幾時死呀仆街<br />\n咁得講得出"},{"pid":"51a3d6a4df4534cc7069652136e391f343de41c2","tid":1739676,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:18:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/12Sll7tqj-A61ECHMt_2BG5RG1nFXTQsO/view\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F12Sll7tqj-A61ECHMt_2BG5RG1nFXTQsO%2Fview&d=UXFjm%2BDMXm%2Fj1yL9MgXeqFDf25aqCgCAAhwKlvpwqyI%3D&h=8f625d22\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/12Sll7tqj-A61ECHMt_2BG5RG1nFXTQsO/view</a>"},{"pid":"26b68070670d9f901f708c79cf4110028609a6de","tid":1739676,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:25:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"384d551bd16d5f86516a648927bf28dac2ef076b","tid":1739676,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T19:28:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}